### 11. `internal/core/user/handler/http/handler.go`

```go
package http

import (
    "net/http"

    "github.com/gin-gonic/gin"
    "github.com/google/uuid"
    "log/slog"

    "github.com/yourusername/yourproject/internal/core/user/service"
